&lt;h1 id=&#34;canyon-scene&#34;&gt;Canyon Scene&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The canyon&amp;rsquo;s textures are actually heavily modified, as the ones that came with the model were green and luscious, so I adjusted them to have that classic red-rock look that many deserts and canyons have.
