&lt;h1 id=&#34;city-scene&#34;&gt;City Scene&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The city scene was a bit different. I ended up using motionless particles to create a huge spawling array of buildings with various properties. The hero buildings were purchased and places in important parts of the scene and were given special attention to detail.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I also created custom window textures including normal maps that make the surface warped just subtly enough to give that subtle rippled look that skyscraper windows have.
